\subtree{
\title{Troubleshooting Common Issues}
\p{\strong{Issue: Dimension mismatch errors} → Check \code{\startverb model.input_dim\stopverb} matches \code{\startverb dataset.node_feature_dim\stopverb} → See \code{\startverb references/core_concepts.md\stopverb} → Essential Attributes}

\p{\strong{Issue: Poor performance on molecular tasks} → Use scaffold splitting, not random → Try GIN instead of GCN → See \code{\startverb references/molecular_property_prediction.md\stopverb} → Best Practices}

\p{\strong{Issue: Protein model not learning} → Use pre-trained ESM for sequence tasks → Check edge construction for structure models → See \code{\startverb references/protein_modeling.md\stopverb} → Training Workflows}

\p{\strong{Issue: Memory errors with large graphs} → Reduce batch size → Use gradient accumulation → See \code{\startverb references/core_concepts.md\stopverb} → Memory Efficiency}

\p{\strong{Issue: Generated molecules are invalid} → Add validity constraints → Post-process with RDKit validation → See \code{\startverb references/molecular_generation.md\stopverb} → Validation and Filtering}
}

